19	// TrackerContentionPreClaimReasonPrefix marks a pre-claim skip caused by
20	// transient multi-worker contention on DDx-managed tracker/metadata files
21	// (.ddx/beads.jsonl, .ddx/metrics/attempts.jsonl, …) rather than a systemic
22	// repo-config problem. Like systemic skips it idles without cooldowning the
23	// bead, but it carries a distinct reason code so operators can tell transient
24	// contention apart from a configuration wedge (ddx-df77e668).
25	const TrackerContentionPreClaimReasonPrefix = "tracker_contention_preclaim:"
